18-Jun-2026 21:46:36 INFO: IP: 127.0.0.1 | ACTIVITY_ID: 6a3404cc03921 | REQUEST TO http://182.23.62.7:8299/service/email METHOD=POST BODY={"to":["adetrihadi@jatelindo.co.id"],"subject":"Kode OTP","body":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" \/>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no\" \/>\n    <title>Kode OTP<\/title>\n    <meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#0092D5\">\n    <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"\/assets\/img\/cropped-Jatelindo-Warna-32x32.webp\" sizes=\"32x32\" \/>\n    <link rel=\"icon\" href=\"\/assets\/img\/cropped-Jatelindo-Warna-192x192.webp\"\n        sizes=\"192x192\" \/>\n    <link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"\/assets\/img\/cropped-Jatelindo-Warna-180x180.webp\" \/>\n    <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"\/assets\/img\/icon-launcher.png\" \/>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https:\/\/fonts.googleapis.com\" \/>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https:\/\/fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin \/>\n    <link href=\"https:\/\/fonts.googleapis.com\/css2?family=Sora:wght@100..800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\" \/>\n    <style>\n    body {\n        font-family: \"Sora\", sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n        background-color: #f4f4f4;\n        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\n    }\n\n    table {\n        border-collapse: collapse !important;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n        width: 80%;\n        max-width: 100%;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        background-color: #ffffff;\n        border-radius: 0;\n        overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .pre-code {\n        background: #f3f3f7;\n        display: block;\n        font-size: 1.2rem;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        letter-spacing: 4px;\n        padding: 10px 12px;\n        border: 1px solid #ebebf2;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        width: fit-content;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n        background-image: url('http:\/\/portal-mis.localhost\/assets\/img\/background-header-email.png');\n        background-size: cover;\n        background-position: top center;\n        background-repeat: no-repeat;\n        color: #ffffff;\n        padding: 32px;\n        margin: 0;\n        display: block;\n    }\n\n    .content-cell {\n        padding: 32px !important;\n        \/* Memaksa padding 32px atas, bawah, kanan, kiri *\/\n        color: #333333;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n        text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    \/* Selector h2 disesuaikan dengan pembungkus barunya *\/\n    .content-cell h2 {\n        margin-top: 0;\n        margin-bottom: 24px;\n        font-size: 20px;\n        color: #000000;\n        font-weight: 400;\n        \/* \"Halo,\" reguler *\/\n        text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    .content-cell h2 strong {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        \/* Variabel bold *\/\n    }\n\n    .content-cell p {\n        margin-top: 0;\n        \/* margin-bottom: 16px; *\/\n        font-size: 14px;\n        color: #1c1c1c;\n        text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    .info-table {\n        width: 100%;\n        margin-top: 16px;\n        border-collapse: collapse;\n    }\n\n    .info-table td {\n        padding: 8px 0;\n        \/* Jarak vertikal antar baris *\/\n        vertical-align: top;\n        font-size: 15px;\n        color: #1c1c1c;\n    }\n\n    .info-table .label {\n        width: 180px;\n        \/* Lebar kolom kiri agar teks muat satu baris *\/\n        white-space: nowrap;\n        \/* Memaksa teks label tetap lurus ke samping *\/\n        font-weight: 400;\n        \/* Memastikan teks kiri TIDAK TEBAL (Reguler) *\/\n    }\n\n    .info-table .colon {\n        width: 20px;\n        \/* Jarak untuk tanda titik dua (:) agar lurus vertikal *\/\n        text-align: center;\n        font-weight: 400;\n        \/* Titik dua tidak tebal *\/\n    }\n\n    .info-table .value {\n        font-weight: 700;\n        \/* Membuat variabel {{...}} di sebelah kanan menjadi TEBAL *\/\n    }\n\n    .label {\n        width: 120px;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    .footer {\n        background-color: #f9f9f9;\n        padding: 24px 32px;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 12px;\n        color: #888888;\n        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;\n    }\n\n    .btn-link {\n        color: #007bff;\n        text-decoration: none;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    .btn-click {\n        display: inline-block;\n        background-color: #3A7BF6;\n        \/* Sesuai Hex di Figma *\/\n        color: #ffffff !important;\n        \/* Warna teks putih *\/\n        font-family: \"Sora\", sans-serif;\n        font-size: 14px;\n        font-weight: 700;\n        \/* Bold *\/\n        text-decoration: none;\n        \/* Menghilangkan garis bawah tautan *\/\n        padding: 10px 16px;\n        \/* Padding sesuai Figma (Top\/Bottom Left\/Right) *\/\n        line-height: 28px;\n        \/* Menjaga total tinggi elemen mendekati 48px *\/\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        \/* Radius sesuai Figma *\/\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    hr {\n        border: 0;\n        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;\n        margin: 30px 0;\n    }\n\n    @media only screen and (min-width: 651px) {\n        body {\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #12161c;\n        }\n\n        .logo-white {\n            display: none !important;\n        }\n\n        .logo-dark {\n            display: block !important;\n        }\n\n        .pre-code {\n            font-size: 1.5rem !important;\n        }\n\n        .text-company {\n            color: #888a8d !important;\n        }\n\n        .text-company,\n        .font-heading,\n        .font-body {\n            font-size: 1rem !important;\n        }\n\n        .font-heading,\n        .font-body {\n            color: #12161c !important;\n        }\n    }\n\n    \/* ==========================================================================\n   Responsive Queries (Mobile \/ Layar Kecil)\n   ========================================================================== *\/\n    @media screen and (max-width: 650px) {\n\n        body {\n            background-color: #ffffff !important;\n        }\n\n        \/* Membalik urutan susunan Header (Logo di atas, teks di bawah) *\/\n        .header-table {\n            display: table !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n        }\n\n        .header-table tr {\n            display: table !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n        }\n\n        .header-table .header-logo {\n            display: table-header-group !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n            text-align: left !important;\n            padding-bottom: 8px !important;\n            \/* Jarak dari logo ke elemen di bawahnya *\/\n        }\n\n        .header-table .header-title {\n            display: table-footer-group !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n            text-align: left !important;\n            font-size: 20px !important;\n            \/* Mengecilkan font jadi 20px *\/\n            padding-top: 18px !important;\n            \/* Memberikan padding top 18px *\/\n        }\n\n        .header-table .header-logo img {\n            margin: 0 !important;\n        }\n\n        \/* --- Perbaikan Info Table Agar Tidak Terpotong di Mobile --- *\/\n        .info-table .label {\n            width: 135px !important;\n            \/* Mempersempit kolom label agar sisa kolom kanan luas *\/\n            white-space: normal !important;\n            font-size: 14px !important;\n        }\n\n        .info-table .colon {\n            width: 15px !important;\n        }\n\n        .info-table .value {\n            font-size: 14px !important;\n            word-break: break-word;\n            \/* Teks variabel panjang otomatis patah baris dengan aman *\/\n        }\n    }\n\n    \/* ==========================================================================\n    Responsive Queries (Dark Mode Global - Dipisah, Tidak Boleh Bersarang)\n   ========================================================================== *\/\n    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n        body {\n            background-color: #2a2d33 !important;\n        }\n\n        .logo-white {\n            display: block !important;\n        }\n\n        .pre-code {\n            background-color: #727272 !important;\n            border-color: #727272 !important;\n        }\n\n        .border-color {\n            border-left: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n            border-right: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n        }\n\n        .border-color-2 {\n            border-left: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n            border-right: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #5a5a5a !important;\n        }\n\n        .hr {\n            margin: 0 !important;\n            padding: 0 !important;\n            border: 1px solid #e7e8e8 !important;\n        }\n\n        .text-company,\n        .font-heading,\n        .font-body {\n            color: #fff !important;\n        }\n    }\n    <\/style>\n<\/head>\n\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n    <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"header-table\">\n        <tr>\n            <td class=\"header-title\" style=\"\n                font-size: 28px;\n                font-weight: bold;\n                color: #ffffff;\n                vertical-align: middle;\n            \">\n                Portal MIS\n            <\/td>\n            <td class=\"header-logo\" align=\"right\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\">\n                <img src=\"http:\/\/portal-mis.localhost\/assets\/img\/img-logo-jatelindo.png\" alt=\"Logo Jatelindo\" style=\"display: block; height: 35px; width: auto\" \/>\n            <\/td>\n        <\/tr>\n    <\/table>\n<\/div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n        <td class=\"content-cell\">        <h2>Halo, <strong>Maker JPA<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n<p>Silakan gunakan kode OTP berikut untuk melanjutkan proses perubahan password. Demi keamanan, jangan\n    bagikan kode kepada siapa pun.<\/p>\n<p>Kode OTP berlaku selama 15 menit.<\/p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 16px;\">\n            <div class=\"pre-code\">\n                <pre style=\"margin: 0\">187402<\/pre>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n<\/table>        <p style=\"margin-top: 16px;\">\n    Terima kasih,<br>\n    <strong>Portal MIS<\/strong>\n<\/p>\n\n<hr \/>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #555555; margin-bottom: 0\">\n    Apabila membutuhkan bantuan atau informasi lebih lanjut, silakan\n    hubungi kami melalui kontak berikut ini:<br \/>\n    <strong>Email :<\/strong> helpdesk@jatelindo.co.id<br \/>\n    <strong>Phone :<\/strong> +628118822249\n<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/table>\n<div class=\"footer\">\n    PT Jatelindo Perkasa Abadi<br \/>\n    Jalan Sunan Kalijaga Blok K5 No.63B, Melawai, Kebayoran Baru, Jakarta\n    Selatan 12160\n<\/div>    <\/div>\n<\/body>\n\n<\/html>","isHtml":true} HEADER={"X-API-KEY":"07575ebb-fb9d-11f0-997f-00163e012243","Content-Type":"application\/json","Authorization":"*****","X-SIGNATURE":"a4a8684499d51d01e72bc9e4d4a8623836e66051d609b38e10028862f6f76c9e"}
